# L9Trends Environment Variables
#
# This project uses separate .env files for each service:
#
# Backend: backend/.env (copy from backend/.env.example)
# Frontend: frontend/.env.local (copy from frontend/.env.example)
#
# 1. cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
# 2. cp frontend/.env.example frontend/.env.local
# 3. Fill in your actual values (Google OAuth credentials, JWT secret, encryption key)
# 4. Run: docker compose up
